<div class="com-share" data-id="18487" data-title="《花5000万在非洲孵化初创企业，微信海外继续抢用户》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/18487/medium/18487.jpg?1449147827" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/18487.html?hmsr=toutiao.io&amp;utm_medium=toutiao.io&amp;utm_source=toutiao.io" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
